cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MS, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method for semantic segmentation and classification of retinal arteries and veins from fundus images using deep learning and graph propagation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of deep learning also suggests the possibility of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The graph propagation technique used in the method may also suggest the possibility of cs.MS (Mathematical Software) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
